Ka la 11 Hlakola 2022, Ramaphosa o tsebiša gore mmušo wa gagwe o tla dira semmušo intasteri ya cannabis ya Afrika Borwa, o nyaka go godiša bobedi tšweletšo le diromelwantle. 

