== Bophelo bja motho ka noši ==
Ramaphosa ke motho wa poraebete kudu gomme ga go tsebje kudu ka bophelo bja gagwe bja motho ka noši. Ramaphosa peleng o be a nyetše Hope Ramaphosa (1978–1989) yoo a nago le morwa le yena, gomme ka morago a nyala le go hlala, mosadi wa kgwebo yo ga bjale a hlokofetšego Nomazizi Mtshotshisa (1991–1993). Ka 1996, o ile a nyala Tshepo Motsepe ,  ngaka ya bongaka le kgaitsedi ya bilione ya meepo ya Afrika Borwa Patrice Motsepe .  Ramaphosa o na le bana ba bahlano bao ba tsebegago. 

O na le ntlo ya maemo a godimo maotong a Hlogo ya Tau ka Motsekapa .  Ramaphosa o tsebega e le yo mongwe wa batho bao ba humilego kudu ka Afrika Borwa, ka lehumo leo le akanyetšwago go feta $ 450 milione gomme o tšweletše ka dimakasineng tša ditšhelete tša go swana le ''Forbes Africa'' le ''Bloomberg'' . 

Ke modumedi wa dipolelo tše dintši , gomme o tsebega ka go akaretša mehutahuta ya maleme a Afrika Borwa ge a neela bontši bja dipolelo tša gagwe. 

